trans-unit.source: The IAccIdentity and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) <xref uid="langword_csharp_IAccIdentity" name="IAccIdentity" href=""></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: IAccIdentity 和所有公开的成员是托管包装的组件对象模型 (COM) 的一部分<xref uid="langword_csharp_IAccIdentity" name="IAccIdentity" href=""></xref>接口。

trans-unit.source: For more information about IAccIdentity, see the documentation for `IAccIdentity::GetIdentityString` in the Microsoft Active Accessibility documentation in the MSDN library at http://msdn.microsoft.com/library.
trans-unit.target: 有关 IAccIdentity 的详细信息，请参阅的文档`IAccIdentity::GetIdentityString`http://msdn.microsoft.com/library 上 MSDN 库中 Microsoft Active Accessibility 文档中。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="Accessibility.IAccIdentity"></xref> and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) <xref uid="langword_csharp_IAccIndentity" name="IAccIndentity" href=""></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="Accessibility.IAccIdentity"> </xref>及其所有公开的成员是否托管包装的组件对象模型 (COM) 的一部分<xref uid="langword_csharp_IAccIndentity" name="IAccIndentity" href=""></xref>接口。

trans-unit.source: For more information about GetIdentityString, see the documentation for `IAccIdentity::GetIdentityString` in the Microsoft Active Accessibility documentation in the MSDN library at http://msdn.microsoft.com/library.
trans-unit.target: 有关 GetIdentityString 的详细信息，请参阅的文档`IAccIdentity::GetIdentityString`http://msdn.microsoft.com/library 上 MSDN 库中 Microsoft Active Accessibility 文档中。

trans-unit.source: Specifies which child of the IAccessible object the caller wants to identify.
trans-unit.target: 指定哪些子 IAccessible 对象调用方想要确定。

trans-unit.source: Address of a variable that receives a pointer to a callee-allocated identity string.
trans-unit.target: 接收一个指针，为被调用方分配的标识字符串的变量的地址。

trans-unit.source: The callee allocates the identity string using <xref uid="langword_csharp_CoTaskMemAlloc" name="CoTaskMemAlloc" href=""></xref>; the caller must release the identity string by using <xref uid="langword_csharp_CoTaskMemFree" name="CoTaskMemFree" href=""></xref> when finished.
trans-unit.target: 被调用方分配标识字符串使用<xref uid="langword_csharp_CoTaskMemAlloc" name="CoTaskMemAlloc" href=""> </xref>; 调用方必须使用版本的标识字符串<xref uid="langword_csharp_CoTaskMemFree" name="CoTaskMemFree" href=""></xref>完成。

trans-unit.source: Address of a variable that receives the length, in bytes, of the callee-allocated identity string.
trans-unit.target: 一个变量来接收长度，以字节为单位，被调用方分配的标识字符串的地址。
